<h2>Fixed responsive containers</h2>

<p>The following classes allow you to specify containers that are fluid until the specified breakpoint is reached and have a <code>max-width</code> from then on. For example, if you prefer a smaller container for a content-centered page.</p>

{% highlight %}
<div class="container-sm">fluid until small breakpoint</div>
<div class="container-md">fluid until medium breakpoint</div>
<div class="container-lg">fluid until large breakpoint</div>
<div class="container-xl">fluid until extra large breakpoint</div>
{% endhighlight %}

