<h2>Fluid container</h2>

<p>If you don't want a container with fixed width per breakpoint, use <code>.container-fluid</code> for a full width container, spanning the entire width of the viewport. With that applied, no <code>max-width</code> is set on the container and it shrinks and grows like any other block element. The left and right space from the viewport is still present.</p>
